FBIS3-23458 "jptot013__l94139" JPRS-TOT-94-013-L Document Type:JPRS Document Title:Terrorism FOUO 24 March 1994 WEST EUROPE TURKEY Bomb Wounds Four in Istanbul's Grand Bazaar NC2403141994 Paris AFP in English 1043 GMT 24 Mar 94 NC2403141994 Paris AFP Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Istanbul, March 24 (AFP) -- A bomb explosion wounded four people Thursday [24 March] in Istanbul's Grand Bazaar, in the heart of the city's historic tourist district, in the second such attack in less than a week, police said. They said a Romanian was among the casualties from the blast which occurred in a ladies' toilet. On Saturday, an explosion in the Haydarpasa train station here left a Singaporese national wounded.
